overview: The user initiated a request for thorough browser-based testing of the
  sleep questionnaire application. The agent systematically navigated through
  the application, testing the questionnaire flow, form validation, conditional
  field rendering, and report generation, including PDF download. It also tested
  the admin login functionality, verifying authentication and error handling.
  API endpoints for responses and PDF generation were also tested, confirming
  correct validation and authentication. The agent successfully identified that
  core functionalities were working as expected, but also found minor issues
  such as ESLint/TypeScript warnings and an outdated page title. It provided a
  detailed summary of its findings and recommendations for cleanup, which the
  user then asked to implement and commit.
